  </p>

  <p>
    What the tool-changer mechanism gives you in practice: true multi-material printing without a wasted tower. You can print flexible TPU seals directly bonded to rigid PETG housings. You can print soluble support material that washes away cleanly. You can print a part in two different colours with no blending or purge waste. This is a different class of capability.
  </p>

  <p>
    Shipping ETA from Snapmaker is April 2026. Pre-orders placed now through 3D3D are queued for setup immediately on arrival.
  </p>

